## Proposed Changes

### Structure
Files to be created in `c:/pixellabs/xyz-college/`:
- `index.html`: Main entry point.
- `css/style.css`: Main stylesheet.
- `js/main.js`: Interaction logic.
- `assets/images/`: Directory for generated images.

